@startuml 5D_Notification_Background_Jobs
title 5-D · Notification Preferences, Delivery & Background Jobs (UC-F43 to UC-F45, UC-S12 to UC-S15)

start
|Registered Fan|
:Open Notifications page;
if (Fan action?) then (View Notifications)
  |System|
  :Load FanNotification list by tenant and fan;
elseif (Fan action?) then (Mark Read)
  :Select notification;
  |System|
  :Set notification read_at = now();
else (Update Preferences)
  :Choose in-app/email notification preferences;
  |System|
  :Save FanNotificationPreference record;
endif

|Fan Event Publisher|
:Publish domain event\n(new post, event, shipment, subscription, payment);

|System|
:Resolve eligible fan audience by tenant,\nvisibility, subscription and preferences;
if (In-app notification enabled?) then (Yes)
  :Create FanNotification record;
else (No)
  :Skip in-app notification;
endif

if (Email notification enabled?) then (Yes)
  :Queue email notification job;
  :Send email through mail provider;
else (No)
  :Skip email;
endif

:Log Fan Activity Audit entry;

|Scheduled Job Runner|
:Run Sync Social Follower Stats job;
|System|
:Fetch follower stats from configured social links;
if (Social sync succeeds?) then (Yes)
  :Update social follower metrics;
else (No)
  :Log sync failure and retry later;
endif

stop
@enduml
